trans-unit.source: Describes encryption and signature requirements that apply to different parts of messages that are transmitted on this channel.
trans-unit.target: 描述加密和簽章需求，這些需求會套用到這個通道上所傳輸訊息的不同部分。

trans-unit.source: When extending the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement> class, you must implement the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement.GetProperty%60%601%28System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext%29> so that it returns an instance of this class corresponding to the binding element.
trans-unit.target: 在擴充 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement> 類別時，您必須實作 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement.GetProperty%60%601%28System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext%29>，這樣它就會傳回這個對應至該繫結項目之類別的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Adds the various parts collections in the specified <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.ChannelProtectionRequirements" /> to the current instance of this class.
trans-unit.target: 將所指定 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.ChannelProtectionRequirements" /> 中的各種部分集合加入至這個類別的目前執行個體。

trans-unit.source: If there are protection requirements for a particular message in both the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.ChannelProtectionRequirements" /> instances, then the requirements are merged together to ensure that the resulting protection requirement is the maximum of the individual protection requirements.
trans-unit.target: 如果這兩個 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Security.ChannelProtectionRequirements" /> 執行個體中的特定訊息都有設定保護需求，這些需求就會合併在一起，以確保最後的保護需求有達到個別保護需求的最大上限。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of this class with incoming and outgoing parts reversed.
trans-unit.target: 建立這個類別的新執行個體，其中的傳入部分和傳出部分彼此互換。

trans-unit.source: A new instance of this class with incoming and outgoing parts reversed.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別的新執行個體，其中的傳入部分和傳出部分彼此互換。

trans-unit.source: Incoming parts of the current instance of this class become outgoing parts of the new instance.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別之目前執行個體的傳入部分，變成新執行個體的傳出部分。

trans-unit.source: Outgoing parts of the current instance of this class become incoming parts of the new instance.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別之目前執行個體的傳出部分，變成新執行個體的傳入部分。

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of message parts that are encrypted for messages from client to server.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether this instance of the class is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，這個值會指出這個類別的執行個體是否是唯讀的。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if this instance of the class is read-only; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果這個類別的執行個體是唯讀的，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 預設值為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Sets this class and its part collections to read-only.
trans-unit.target: 將這個類別及其部分集合設定成唯讀的。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ChannelProtectionRequirements.IsReadOnly%2A> is set to true, as are the corresponding properties on the parts collections.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ChannelProtectionRequirements.IsReadOnly%2A> 會設定為 true，這個值與部分集合上的對應屬性相同。
